{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Laser Sword Fight - Cut Everything</strong></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Slice5_Steam2.gif?t=1604755116\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Slice7_Steam2.gif?t=1604755116\" /><br>Fight various enemies with a laser sword. Advanced physics engine allows you to cut every object into pieces, there is no limit, you can cut through everything!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Use Your Power</strong></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Steam_Power_300x200.gif?t=1604755116\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Steam_Throw_300x200.gif?t=1604755116\" /><br>Use your power to push and pull objects and smash enemies with heavy boxes. Throw the Saber with a satisfying spinning effect! Unleash unlimited power!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Defend With Style</strong></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Defend1_Steam2.gif?t=1604755116\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Defend2_Steam2.gif?t=1604755116\" /><br>Deflect enemy fire with your blade! Use two different techniques for different behavior. Master your dodge abilities and raise your fighting style even higher!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choose Your Saber</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208770/extras/Banner_Saber_Purple.png?t=1604755116\" /><br>A single blade? Double blade? Reverse grip? Maybe dual wield?<br>Use the in-game workshop to customize your Blade and Hilt.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Random Level Generation</strong></h2><i